<bibRefCitation id="C9034B24FF9E2E3E5E5768C432C2FB21" author="Sobral, M. &amp; Lucas, E. &amp; Landrum, L. &amp; Soares-Silva, L." box="[543,765,1245,1271]" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" pagination="352 - 366" refId="ref15003" refString="Sobral, M., Lucas, E., Landrum, L. &amp; Soares-Silva, L. (2009) Myrtaceae. In: Stehmann, J., Forzza, R. C., Salino, A., Sobral, M., Costa, D. P. &amp; Kamino, L. H. Y. Plantas da Floresta Atlantica. Rio de Janeiro, pp 352 - 366." type="book chapter" year="2009">
Sobral 
<emphasis id="9FE6EAC7FF9E2E3E5E3168C73289FB21" box="[633,694,1246,1271]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="43">et al.</emphasis>
2009
</bibRefCitation>
) in the northeastern and southeastern regions of 
<collectingCountry id="D5857645FF9E2E3E591A68C435A3FB21" box="[1362,1436,1245,1271]" name="Brazil" pageId="10" pageNumber="43">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="C9034B24FF9E2E3E5CD6691A318AFACB" author="Proenca, C. E. B. &amp; Sobral, M." box="[158,437,1283,1309]" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" pagination="111 - 113" refId="ref14537" refString="Proenca, C. E. B. &amp; Sobral, M. (2006) Myrtaceae, In: Barbosa, M. R. V., Sothers, C., Mayo, S., Gamarra-Rojas, C. F. L. &amp; Mesquita, A. C. (eds.). Checklist das Plantas do Nordeste Brasileiro: Angiospermas e Gymnospermas. Ministerio de Ciencia e Tecnologia, Brasilia, pp. 111 - 113." type="book chapter" year="2006">Proença &amp; Sobral 2006</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="C9034B24FF9E2E3E5D89691A32A8FACB" author="Sobral, M. &amp; Proenca, C. &amp; Souza, M. &amp; Mazine, F. &amp; Lucas, E." box="[449,663,1283,1309]" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" refId="ref15080" refString="Sobral, M., Proenca, C., Souza, M., Mazine, F. &amp; Lucas, E. (2010) Myrtaceae. In: Forzza, R. C., Leitman, P. M., Costa, A. F., Carvalho Jr., A. A., Peixoto, A. L., Walter, B. M. T., Bicudo, C., Zappi, D., Costa, D. P., Lleras, E., Martinelli, G., Lima, H. C., Prado, J., Stehmann, J. R., Baumgratz, J. F. A., Pirani, J. R., Sylvestre, L., Maia, L. C., Lohmann, L. G., Queiroz, L. P., Silveira, M., Coelho, M. N., Mamede, M. C., Bastos, M. N. C., Morim, M. P., Barbosa, M. R., Menezes, M., Hopkins, M., Secco, R., Cavalcanti, T. B. &amp; Souza, V. C. Lista de Especies da Flora do Brasil. Jardim Botanico do Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro. Published on the internet; http: // floradobrasil. jbrj. gov. br / 2010 / FB 010791. Accessed: 5 October 2011." type="url" year="2010">
Sobral 
<emphasis id="9FE6EAC7FF9E2E3E5E5D691A326FFACA" box="[533,592,1283,1308]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="43">et al.</emphasis>
2010
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AD2D36D5FF9E2E3E5C8E693034EAFA58" blockId="10.[151,1436,1206,1534]" pageId="10" pageNumber="43">
Trees and shrubs 
<quantity id="6A6A9B30FF9E2E3E5DDD693031DFFA95" box="[405,480,1321,1347]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" unit="m" value="5.0" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="3.0">3–7 m</quantity>
tall. Morphologicaly similar to 
<taxonomicName id="6A924D56FF9E2E3E5F11693033C6FA94" authorityName="Sobral" authorityYear="2006" baseAuthorityName="DC." box="[857,1017,1321,1346]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" phylum="Magnoliopsida" rank="species" species="densa">
<emphasis id="9FE6EAC7FF9E2E3E5F11693033C6FA94" box="[857,1017,1321,1346]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="43">Myrcia densa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but differs by having larger leaves (
<quantity id="6A6A9B30FF9E2E3E5CD769573137FABE" box="[159,264,1358,1384]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" unit="cm" value="7.5" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="5.0">5–10 cm</quantity>
long), acute calyx lobes and a pilose hypanthium; it differs from other 
<taxonomicName id="6A924D56FF9E2E3E581069573536FABE" box="[1112,1289,1358,1384]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="10" pageNumber="43" phylum="Magnoliopsida" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="9FE6EAC7FF9E2E3E581069573493FAB1" box="[1112,1196,1358,1383]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="43">Myrcia</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
by having a non-sulcate midvein on the adaxial lamina surface, ferruginous trichomes and globose fruits.
</paragraph>
